Environment variable OPTICKSDEPENDENCIES should point to a directory with the following:
   Boost - 1.33...do not compile, used in #include mode.
   Cg - 1.4.1
   ffmpeg - Subversion trunk revision 6181 with local changes.
   glew - 1.3.4
   Hdf4 -
   Hdf5 - 1.6.5
   libjpeg - 6b
   libgeotiff - 1.2.3
   libproj4 - 4.4.9
   libtiff - 3.8.1
   OoModtran - 2.0
   ossim - CVS-21Aug06 with local changes
   pthreads - 2.7.0...only needed on windows platforms
   Qt - 4.2.3 with local changes..local changes include patches from trolltech which have not been
                                  incorporated into 4.2.3. Contact the Opticks team for a list of patches.
   qwt - 5.0.0rc0
   ShapeLib - 1.2.10
   Xerces - 2.7.0
   zlib - 1.2.3
Any merged "with local changes" indicate patches may be required...contact the Opticks team for further
information. Not all packages will build cleanly on all platforms without changes (usually x64).
In a directory structure that matches the following. Cases with a platform name indicate files specific to
that platform. The files correspond to the installed layout of the applicable package unless otherwise noted.

